{"tid":291772,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"倉鼠走甩左⋯","createTime":"2017-06-20T23:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T00:39:13.000Z","uid":16685,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"360610a07015bdf9a21801fe49af44b19bd27d22","tid":291772,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T23:54:49.000Z","msg":"個寵放左係個48吋櫃上面<br />\n岩先番到屋企見到個籠對門開左就知奶撚左野<br />\n走失左⋯<br />\n可以肯定既係佢無襯我開門既時候走左出外面，<br />\n但搵雲全屋都見唔到佢既蹤影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所有櫃底雪櫃底陰角都搵過哂<br />\n由咁高跌落黎一定好傷<br />\n依加放左啲糧係膠袋上面，希望佢會過去食，發出啲聲等我聽到<br />\n但我岩岩收完工好眼訓想訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 隔幾個鐘又要出去開工<br />\n希望佢平平安安無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913eb0757d7a8a0a69941b58bcbc49492580d5f7","tid":291772,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T23:56:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7019fab0796ac3e9154d0b1b2267b6b08642425","tid":291772,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T23:56:55.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以教我點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12901a3fc59f0ebf43bb31e70a9b242cf9320b09","tid":291772,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T23:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/21/075734_a4508fffa49125834b11aaadd991f5ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F21%2F075734_a4508fffa49125834b11aaadd991f5ab.jpg&h=18aedf27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買左番黎先兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 熊仔鼠黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c69028d30a5531a9a63abcbc4453c314cf80f4","tid":291772,"uid":71251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T23:59:59.000Z","msg":"周圍擺野食餓佢會出黎"},{"pid":"20f895cb30b71242b65d83fff1f0805ee2ce281f","tid":291772,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>周圍擺野食餓佢會出黎</blockquote><br />\n萬一我出左街果陣先出黎咁點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c3738a41fdaaf7f793f7ed1db5161a36010948","tid":291772,"uid":10342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:16:37.000Z","msg":"平時有無訓練佢 <br />\n聽到膠袋聲=有野食？<br />\n如果有就好快搵到"},{"pid":"8e7cacff86d9520be3b03d1f1f038e9b7fd16a82","tid":291772,"uid":91585,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:25:49.000Z","msg":"可能去左搵哈姆朋友姐,唔洗咁唔開心<br />\n會自己番黎"},{"pid":"67cc8b95c979e10fcc82a900b17762c97ea4b041","tid":291772,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能去左搵哈姆朋友姐,唔洗咁唔開心<br />\n會自己番黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beffac9b48d8c6466519e81e9af5cf6663911c8d","tid":291772,"uid":33031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:47:24.000Z","msg":"有冇搵過d 拿位呀"},{"pid":"678905ca67e7b14e0cc48b95ea44769aa174a017","tid":291772,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:55:02.000Z","msg":"搵番了各位，已經用野封死個籠"},{"pid":"249e47ab7b98a1b7ed984a3ca2682bde9d6e91b7","tid":291772,"uid":51330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:15:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可能去左搵哈姆朋友姐,唔洗咁唔開心<br />\n會自己番黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src